stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> Draft : New Invoice Generated (CRM: Linked to Opportunity/Account)
    Draft --> PendingApproval : Submit for Approval (CRM: Internal Task/Notification to Approver)
    PendingApproval --> Draft : Rejected (CRM: Task Re-assigned, Notification to Creator)
    PendingApproval --> ReadyToSend : Approved (CRM: Invoice Status Updated)

    ReadyToSend --> Sent : Send to Customer (CRM: Activity Log 'Invoice Sent', Email Template Used)
    Sent --> Viewed : Customer Viewed Invoice (CRM: Email Tracking, Activity Log 'Invoice Viewed')
    Sent --> AwaitingPayment : Payment Term Begins (e.g., Net 30)
    Viewed --> AwaitingPayment : Payment Term Begins

    AwaitingPayment --> PartiallyPaid : Partial Payment Received (CRM: Payment Record Updated, Activity Log)
    AwaitingPayment --> Paid : Full Payment Received (CRM: Payment Record, Opportunity Status 'Paid')

    PartiallyPaid --> Paid : Remaining Payment Received (CRM: Payment Record, Opportunity Status 'Paid')
    PartiallyPaid --> Overdue : Due Date Passed (CRM: Automated Reminder/Task for Account Manager)

    AwaitingPayment --> Overdue : Due Date Passed (CRM: Automated Reminder/Task for Account Manager)
    Overdue --> Paid : Full Payment Received (CRM: Payment Record, Opportunity Status 'Paid')

    Sent --> Disputed : Customer Raises Dispute (CRM: Case Created, Account Task for Resolution)
    AwaitingPayment --> Disputed : Customer Raises Dispute (CRM: Case Created, Account Task)
    Overdue --> Disputed : Customer Raises Dispute (CRM: Case Created, Account Task)
    PartiallyPaid --> Disputed : Customer Raises Dispute (CRM: Case Created, Account Task)

    Disputed --> Sent : Resolution: Re-issue/Re-send (CRM: New Invoice Version, Activity Log)
    Disputed --> Paid : Resolution: Payment Received (CRM: Payment Record, Opportunity Status 'Paid')
    Disputed --> Cancelled : Resolution: Voided Invoice (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled')

    Draft --> Cancelled : Voided Before Sending (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled')
    PendingApproval --> Cancelled : Voided Before Sending (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled')
    ReadyToSend --> Cancelled : Voided Before Sending (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled')
    Sent --> Cancelled : Voided After Sending (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled', Notifications)
    AwaitingPayment --> Cancelled : Voided (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled')
    PartiallyPaid --> Cancelled : Voided (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled')
    Overdue --> Cancelled : Voided (CRM: Invoice Status 'Cancelled')

    Paid --> Refunded : Payment Refunded (CRM: Refund Record, Activity Log, Notification)

    Cancelled --> [*] : Final State (CRM: Reporting Excludes)
    Refunded --> [*] : Final State (CRM: Reporting Excludes)
    Paid --> [*] : Final State (CRM: Revenue Recognized)